name: 本特利·斯托尔特布姆
name_full: 本特利·斯托尔特布姆 Bentley Storteboom
introduction: Bentley is a Canadian Television and Commercial actor. Mostly known for playing Dagwood in the hit TV show CW's Riverdale and playing Jared Padalecki son is CW's Supernatural. He started acting at the age of 7 and fell in love with story telling and being on set. Bentley has been in acting training for 2 years, and love every moment. He is professional, affectionate and has a zest for life. You can follow him on Instagram: bentley_storteboom
